Noto Sans Ethiopic ExtCond Blk Regular (NotoSansEthiopic-ExtraCondensedBlack.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

(NID 16 + 'Space' + NID 17) 'Noto Sans Ethiopic ExtraCondensed Black' ≠ 'Noto Sans Ethiopic ExtCond Blk' (NID 1).
